    "In this subsection, we aim to align the community's understanding of this term and clearly distinguish between CF-based methods.",
    "In the context of NLP, we adopt the following definition, which captures the fundamental characteristic common to all CF-based methods: \"a counterfactual for a given textual example is a result of a targeted intervening on the text while holding everything else equal.\"",
